Bugs
====
* Invalid .mli files created when no attributes are used

Requested
=========
* Better reporting of syntax errors in parsing grammar
* Wide chars / unicode / character classes
* Canonify is not idempotent
* Case-insensitive matching
* Use a threaded interpreter

Granted
=======
* Implicit concatenation of tokens with a space operator ; method for escaping this default (e.g. concatenated(..))
* Namespaces / prefixes
* Better error reporting (backtrace) - error_position()

Rejected
========
